          <p>We build with AI-accelerated workflows from the start. Every engineer uses AI coding assistants, automated testing, and intelligent code review. Test-driven development ensures quality. Pull requests get peer-reviewed and AI-scanned before merge. The result: production-ready code shipped 3x faster.</p>
